text.text: Go up ramps to trigger cutscene.
Complete tutorial, you'll end up in your house afterwards.
Exit house, talk to everyone (Young man, young boy, teenage boy, old man, young woman).
Check Transer of young woman, young boy, young man, teenage boy.
Grab GrassStage BMW. Folder edit. Equip BublFist.
Fight Jammer at top of Comp.
Pulse out, head home and go to sleep.
Go to your spot at Vista Point.
Head back to Echo Ridge. You'll be pulsed in after th cutscene.
Go to top of comp, interact with control panel. Forced fight.
Follow red path to grab 700z BMW and RedKey. Exit and re-enter comp.
Follow blue path to grab BlueKey. Exist and re-enter comp.
Follow yellow path to grab YellowKey.
